title: Kill Bill Vol. 1 (HC Eng where needed)
description:
I enjoy watching on my Blu-Ray player, but it doesn't do external subs very
well & I'm guessing I'm not alone in that department. So here it is English
Hardcoded, where there is non English dialogue. Optional custom English soft
subs for the entire film (Spanish, Japanese, Korean & Chinese too).


The Bride wakens from a four-year coma. The child she carried in her womb is gone. Now she must wreak vengeance on the team of assassins who betrayed her - a team she was once part of. Rated R
